Arsenal's players have gotten into the festive spirit by selecting their favourite Christmas songs ahead of the big day on December 25.

A number of Gunners players took part and named their No 1 festive songs with Jingle Bells by James Lord Pierpont proving a popular selection.

Jack Wilshere, Mathieu Debuchy, Mikel Arteta and Calum Chambers all chose that song, while Kieran Gibbs and Wojciech Szczesny selection Brenda Lee's Rockin' around the Christmas tree .

